description:
After months of applying, job seekers are finally landing interviews… only to be met with malfunctioning AI instead of real people.

#AIInterviews #TechUnderCapitalism #Automation #FutureOfWork #JobInterview 

I am creating these videos for entertainment and educational purposes. Please do not contact or harass any individuals featured in the clips. These clips are included to critique broader trends in the tech industry, particularly where innovation is used to justify exploitative or user-unfriendly practices. I do not condone online bullying or harassment in any form. 

If you enjoyed this content, please consider subscribing to the channel!

All thoughts and opinions are my own. 

Chapters: 
00:00 Intro
00:26 Dream Job Interview
02:40 Dream Job Follow Up
05:51 AI Phone Interview
07:55 Malfunctioning German AI
10:44 AI Recording
15:25 AI Interviewing Other AI
17:16 Don’t Work at These Companies
19:47 AI Interviews are Unnatural
21:27 Club Pilates AI Interview
22:28 Another Club Pilates AI Interview
24:07 Apriora AI Interviewer
26:41 Humans Finding Humor
